            <title>WordPress GenAI Plus - AI Content Generation Plugin</title>
            <link>http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/</link>
            <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate>
            <guid>http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/</guid>
            <description>&lt;p&gt;Generative AI (GenAI) has risen rapidly since 2022, sweeping the globe and demonstrating enormous potential across multiple domains — text-to-image, text-to-text, image-to-image, and more. Models like Stable Diffusion and DALL-E can generate realistic images from natural-language descriptions, opening new possibilities for creative design and visual arts. Meanwhile, large language models such as Claude and GPT enable natural, fluent conversational interactions, empowering content creation and Q&amp;amp;A applications.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;WordPress is a widely used open-source content management system (CMS) ideal for creating and managing all types of websites — blogs, corporate sites, personal pages, and online stores. First released in 2003, it was designed to give users an easy-to-use platform for publishing content, even without a technical background.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Now, leveraging the powerful AI capabilities of AWS, you can experience an intelligent AI writing assistant directly inside WordPress to accelerate your content creation. The newly launched WordPress GenAI Plus solution seamlessly integrates Claude 3 (via Amazon Bedrock) and Stable Diffusion into the WordPress editor. Simply provide a prompt or topic direction, and the AI will automatically generate article content and images. You can iterate as many times as needed until you achieve the ideal result.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The main features provided by WordPress GenAI Plus writing assistant include:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Text Generation&lt;/strong&gt;: Generate articles based on user prompts&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Image Generation&lt;/strong&gt;: Generate images based on user prompts&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Translation&lt;/strong&gt;: Currently supports Chinese, English, French, Japanese, and Korean as target languages; source language is unrestricted&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grammar Check&lt;/strong&gt;: Provides grammar correction suggestions for selected English paragraphs (English only)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This solution supports one-click deployment via an Amazon CloudFormation template. By deploying the stack, users get the complete infrastructure — WordPress site, database, CDN, and AI capabilities — greatly simplifying setup and usage.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;architecture-overview&#34;&gt;Architecture Overview&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;The WordPress GenAI Plus solution can be deployed in any AWS global region. It offers both a two-tier architecture (separating web and database layers) and a traditional LNMP (Linux, Nginx, MySQL, PHP) all-in-one architecture. The two-tier architecture is shown below:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Two-tier architecture&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;297px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;124&#34; height=&#34;2451&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img1.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img1_hu_ef986cc92121e38c.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img1_hu_1f38168aeec108de.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img1_hu_9cb7cba0cd6786a8.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img1.jpg 3042w&#34; width=&#34;3042&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Architecture highlights: Two-tier (web + data), WordPress on public subnet, RDS on private subnet, multi-AZ option, CloudFront CDN, Lambda + Bedrock integration for GenAI capabilities. EC2, RDS, and Lambda can be deployed in any region; Bedrock is available in us-east-1 or us-west-2.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;deployment-process&#34;&gt;Deployment Process&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;model-access-preparation&#34;&gt;Model Access Preparation&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Before getting started, you need to request model access permissions in Amazon Bedrock.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Select the Bedrock service in the AWS global console&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Select Bedrock service&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;423px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;176&#34; height=&#34;1632&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img2.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img2_hu_ff7adb1de6e28a7c.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img2_hu_ed60cc0f95369656.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img2_hu_eb0db7bf6f95213e.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img2.jpg 2880w&#34; width=&#34;2880&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Select the model deployment region (us-east-1 or us-west-2) in the top-right corner&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Select region&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;424px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;176&#34; height=&#34;1628&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img3.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img3_hu_c6dbf5acc69a53a.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img3_hu_690ac4e1519353c2.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img3_hu_7ffe6cbb83d97648.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img3.jpg 2880w&#34; width=&#34;2880&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;In the left sidebar, select &amp;ldquo;Model access&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Model access&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;426px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;177&#34; height=&#34;1622&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img4.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img4_hu_eb5eae4fa56907c.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img4_hu_2084e03a8b9945a9.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img4_hu_8bbe8fe229be6d5f.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img4.jpg 2880w&#34; width=&#34;2880&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Click the &amp;ldquo;Manage model access&amp;rdquo; button&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Manage model access&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;602px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;250&#34; height=&#34;1148&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img5.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img5_hu_4c7e1fcce0773894.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img5_hu_914817e58e4a3a46.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img5_hu_9c6dc810c37010b5.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img5.jpg 2880w&#34; width=&#34;2880&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Check the boxes for SDXL1.0, Claude 3 Sonnet, and Claude 3 Haiku, then click &amp;ldquo;Save changes&amp;rdquo;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Select models&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;462px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;192&#34; height=&#34;1368&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img6.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img6_hu_78eff3ca9133ee4f.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img6_hu_d3ad62343717f74c.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img6_hu_cc484afaeb398a9b.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img6.jpg 2634w&#34; width=&#34;2634&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Wait for permission to be granted (status changes to &amp;ldquo;Access granted&amp;rdquo;)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-key-pair&#34;&gt;Create Key Pair&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;A key pair allows you to securely connect to your Amazon EC2 instance via SSH. Before deployment, make sure you have created a key pair.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;If you haven&amp;rsquo;t created one yet, &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://console.aws.amazon.com/ec2/home?#CreateKeyPair:&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;click here to create a key pair&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Create key pair&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;421px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;175&#34; height=&#34;1617&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img7.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img7_hu_cad5c45fa3e0a90d.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img7_hu_f6cce1f57c16990f.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img7_hu_94281de5e7298609.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img7.jpg 2842w&#34; width=&#34;2842&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Confirm the deployment region, enter a key pair name, click &amp;ldquo;Create key pair&amp;rdquo; and save it securely.&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;create-cloudformation-stack&#34;&gt;Create CloudFormation Stack&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Click the link above to enter the stack deployment page.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://console.aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/home?#stacks/create/template?templateURL=https://aws-cn-getting-started.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/wordpress-plus/WordpressTwoLayer.template.json&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Click to deploy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Confirm the deployment region in the top-right corner (must match your key pair region), then specify the following parameters:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Custom stack name&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;EC2 instance type&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;EC2 disk size&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;EC2 key pair&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Database username&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Database password (min 8 chars, no /, quotes, or @)&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Database instance type&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Database storage size&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Multi-AZ deployment option&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Bedrock deployment region&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Click Next.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Parameter configuration 1&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;437px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;182&#34; height=&#34;1482&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img8.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img8_hu_7d2b2c9cef5c41c6.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img8_hu_421e9f77cd018aa8.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img8_hu_439213e3bdf1cd13.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img8.jpg 2701w&#34; width=&#34;2701&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Parameter configuration 2&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;340px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;141&#34; height=&#34;1481&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img9.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img9_hu_6288bdd7fec4c900.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img9_hu_b4fcc6939852e6fa.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img9.jpg 2103w&#34; width=&#34;2103&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;On step 3 &amp;ldquo;Configure stack options&amp;rdquo;, click Next&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Configure stack options&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;468px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;195&#34; height=&#34;1267&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img10.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img10_hu_95518abbf47e5ca7.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img10_hu_fb67f51952fa9f00.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img10_hu_2115bc5a21c35a03.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img10.jpg 2471w&#34; width=&#34;2471&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;On step 4, check the IAM acknowledgments and CAPABILITY_AUTO_EXPAND, then click Submit&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Confirm and submit&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;1388px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;578&#34; height=&#34;334&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img11.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img11_hu_3d90c68d964ed45.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img11_hu_ff83e94cfa74f7ac.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img11.jpg 1933w&#34; width=&#34;1933&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Wait about 10 minutes for the stack status to become CREATE_COMPLETE&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Creating&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;286px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;119&#34; height=&#34;946&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img12.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img12_hu_81f94874089ae4dd.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img12.jpg 1129w&#34; width=&#34;1129&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Creation complete&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;1107px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;461&#34; height=&#34;273&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img13.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img13_hu_3781969cab94306a.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img13.jpg 1260w&#34; width=&#34;1260&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;Check the Outputs tab for GenAI Function URL, WordPress install URL, admin URL, and site URL&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Outputs&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;496px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;206&#34; height=&#34;537&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img14.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img14_hu_353ab9d564899a99.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img14.jpg 1111w&#34; width=&#34;1111&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;start-using-wordpress-ai-capabilities&#34;&gt;Start Using WordPress AI Capabilities&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;initialize-wordpress&#34;&gt;Initialize WordPress&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;After deployment, find the InstallWordPress field in the CloudFormation stack outputs and open the URL to configure WordPress.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Install WordPress&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;746px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;310&#34; height=&#34;926&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img15.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img15_hu_bf06d4c5c6828201.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img15_hu_481036577f33f7d8.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img15_hu_2d7b049f3e10d176.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img15.jpg 2879w&#34; width=&#34;2879&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In the one-click deployment, database information is pre-configured. You only need to set up your site title, username, and password, then click &amp;ldquo;Install WordPress&amp;rdquo; and log into the admin panel.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Configure site info&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;223px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;93&#34; height=&#34;1758&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img16.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img16_hu_86e385ae7faafc9c.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img16_hu_641f58c03ebd0476.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img16.jpg 1639w&#34; width=&#34;1639&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;enable-the-genai-plugin&#34;&gt;Enable the GenAI Plugin&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the WordPress admin panel, click &amp;ldquo;Plugins&amp;rdquo;, find &amp;ldquo;Amazon AI writing assistant&amp;rdquo; and click Activate.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Enable plugin&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;400px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;166&#34; height=&#34;1083&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img17.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img17_hu_efdbd2773c46eb06.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img17_hu_e62b2ca4d64d37f7.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img17.jpg 1805w&#34; width=&#34;1805&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The Lambda URL and Region are pre-configured. Verify and click Save.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Plugin configuration&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;456px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;190&#34; height=&#34;1388&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img18.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img18_hu_56798583b4336e7f.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img18_hu_a787804102fa7bcf.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img18_hu_f4020940aeba884f.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img18.jpg 2641w&#34; width=&#34;2641&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h3 id=&#34;experience-genai-capabilities&#34;&gt;Experience GenAI Capabilities&#xA;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;In the WordPress admin, click &amp;ldquo;New → Post&amp;rdquo;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;New post&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;457px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;190&#34; height=&#34;586&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img19.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img19_hu_824c0100d2ea8ab7.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img19.jpg 1118w&#34; width=&#34;1118&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;In the editor body, type &lt;code&gt;/ask&lt;/code&gt; to trigger the Ask AI plugin. Click it to start using the AI features.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Ask AI plugin&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;658px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;274&#34; height=&#34;426&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img20.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img20_hu_71405a2822eef0f3.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img20.jpg 1168w&#34; width=&#34;1168&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;You can enter text-to-text or text-to-image prompts in Chinese or English in the popup input box.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Text generation example&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;766px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;319&#34; height=&#34;432&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img21.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img21_hu_e2be7a30c6459c1b.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img21.jpg 1380w&#34; width=&#34;1380&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Image generation example&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;778px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;324&#34; height=&#34;401&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img22.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img22_hu_21aebfa7b3e7210c.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img22.jpg 1300w&#34; width=&#34;1300&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;See the demo below:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;GenAI demo&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;368px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;153&#34; height=&#34;521&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/gif1.gif&#34; width=&#34;800&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;The GenAI plugin also supports translation and grammar checking:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Translation&lt;/strong&gt;: Enter text in any language, click the pen icon in the floating toolbar → Translate Text. Target language is set in the plugin configuration page. Supported: ZH_CN, EN_US, FR, JA, KO.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Translation demo&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;417px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;173&#34; height=&#34;345&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/gif2.gif&#34; width=&#34;600&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Translation config&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;428px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;178&#34; height=&#34;1400&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img25.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img25_hu_6826f283d45e92c0.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img25_hu_c1733b4c18dafc5e.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img25_hu_6e5b049473cfecbd.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img25.jpg 2500w&#34; width=&#34;2500&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Grammar Check&lt;/strong&gt;: For text you want to correct, click the pen icon in the floating toolbar → Correct Text.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;Grammar check demo&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;417px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;173&#34; height=&#34;345&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/gif3.gif&#34; width=&#34;600&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;alternative-architecture&#34;&gt;Alternative Architecture&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;You can configure your own domain name in Amazon CloudFront, use Certificate Manager to request a free public certificate for HTTPS, and update the site address in the WordPress admin panel.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;This solution also supports a traditional LNMP all-in-one WordPress architecture:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img alt=&#34;LNMP architecture&#34; class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; data-flex-basis=&#34;709px&#34; data-flex-grow=&#34;295&#34; height=&#34;1259&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; sizes=&#34;(max-width: 767px) calc(100vw - 30px), (max-width: 1023px) 700px, (max-width: 1279px) 950px, 1232px&#34; src=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img27.jpg&#34; srcset=&#34;http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img27_hu_1a9e40034b81b345.jpg 800w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img27_hu_959d415c4d7de88c.jpg 1600w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img27_hu_b44b6ce634ac4395.jpg 2400w, http://localhost:4002/p/wordpress-genai-plus/images/img27.jpg 3721w&#34; width=&#34;3721&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Deploy the LNMP architecture: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://console.aws.amazon.com/cloudformation/home?#stacks/create/template?templateURL=https://aws-cn-getting-started.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/wordpress-plus/WordpressInOne.template.json&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;Click to deploy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;h2 id=&#34;summary&#34;&gt;Summary&#xA;&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Through this tutorial, you can deploy WordPress GenAI Plus on AWS with one click, integrating the power of generative AI into the WordPress editor for a brand-new AI-powered content creation experience.&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;Related Resources:&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&lt;ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/cn/campaigns/aigc&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;AWS AIGC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#xA;&lt;/ul&gt;&#xA;&lt;hr&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;blockquote&gt;&#xA;        &lt;p&gt;Original article: &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://aws.amazon.com/cn/blogs/china/wordpress-genai-plus-accelerate-your-website-content-creation-with-generative-ai/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&#xA;    &gt;WordPress GenAI Plus: Accelerate Your Website Content Creation with Generative AI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&#xA;&#xA;    &lt;/blockquote&gt;&#xA;</description>
